sentences: Tyler James Hilton (born November 22, 1983) is an American singer-songwriter and actor.
Hilton began his professional career in music in 2000.
Rolling Stone magazine compared him to his contemporary, Howie Day, while others have compared Hilton to Elton John, both vocally and instrumentally.
He also appeared in Taylor Swift's music video "Teardrops on My Guitar" and Gloriana's music video "(Kissed You) Good Night".
Early years and personal life ==
Hilton was born in Palm Springs, California, the son of Kristy (née Herren) and Robert George Hilton.
After a brief stint in Northern California, his family moved back to the Palm Springs area, where he wrote his first song about a girl named Rhian with whom he attended school.
